10:41.975 --> 10:47.013 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
are basically in areas which are
completely surrounded by

10:47.046 --> 10:51.684 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
checkpoints and where different
fighting parties are not

10:51.718 --> 10:55.388 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
allowing humanitarian assistance
to get through. WARNER: U.S.

10:55.421 --> 10:58.458 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
officials hope these talks will
lead to a permanent cease fire

10:58.491 --> 11:02.128 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and a flow of aid. Today,
negotiators did agree to let

11:02.161 --> 11:06.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
supplies into hard-hit Taiz and
elsewhere. And Houthis and

11:06.666 --> 11:11.070 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
