exchanged hundreds of prisoners.

11:11.104 --> 11:14.874 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But a political settlement of
this devastating conflict still

11:14.908 --> 11:21.014 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
looks far away. SUBTITLE: In
Yemen, 19 million people lack

11:21.047 --> 11:26.052 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
