fishing, I drop everything and

20:07.473 --> 20:11.310 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
go to help, because my work is
not as important as saving human

20:11.343 --> 20:15.948 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
lives. The worst thing is the
drowned people, drowned mothers,

20:15.981 --> 20:21.087 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
drowned children. BRABANT: One
of the worst days was in late

20:21.120 --> 20:26.025 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
October when a boat carrying 300
people capsized. More than 30,

20:26.058 --> 20:28.861 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
including several children, lost
their lives. UNIDENTIFIED

20:28.894 --> 20:33.899 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
FEMALE: Five, six, seven, eight,
nine, 10, 11, 12, 14, 15 --

20:38.104 --> 20:41.207 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
FINTERIS: The pictures I saw
during those incidents which I

20:41.240 --> 20:44.210 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
was seeing almost on a daily
basis would come back to me

20:44.243 --> 20:47.379 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
