26:11.103 --> 26:13.972 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Sreenivasan. HARI SREENIVASAN,
PBS NEWSHOUR ANCHOR: On August

26:14.006 --> 26:17.409 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
11, 2008, an 18-year old
Washington woman reported she

26:17.443 --> 26:21.547 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
