is no indication that police

27:06.925 --> 27:11.430 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
doubt the truth of what she is
telling them. But quickly, as

27:11.463 --> 27:15.567 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
soon as one day after, she
reports being raped, doubts set

27:15.601 --> 27:19.538 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
in. And it really originates
with the call that comes into

27:19.571 --> 27:23.675 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the police station from the
woman's foster mother. The

27:23.709 --> 27:27.179 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
foster mother says that she has
questions about whether this had

27:27.212 --> 27:30.315 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
really happened. She wonders if
maybe this was a bid for

27:30.349 --> 27:33.852 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
