false police report.

28:22.367 --> 28:24.336 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SREENIVASAN: Now, this is all
happening in Linwood,

28:24.369 --> 28:26.905 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
