connect to a case in Colorado?

28:26.939 --> 28:32.978 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ARMSTRONG: Well, after she
admits to making the story up,

28:33.011 --> 28:37.649 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
she takes a plea deal in which
she agrees to certain conditions

28:37.683 --> 28:42.220 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
