28:42.254 --> 28:46.091 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
raped. And she agrees to go on
supervised probation for a year.

28:46.124 --> 28:49.995 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Two and a half years later, two
and a half years after she is

28:50.028 --> 28:53.465 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
charged with filing a false
police report, a serial rapist

28:53.498 --> 28:58.003 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
is arrested in Colorado. And
when police execute a search

28:58.036 --> 29:01.607 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
