that he had, indeed, raped Marie

29:07.613 --> 29:11.049 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
in Linwood two and a half years
before. SREENIVASAN: And then

29:11.083 --> 29:14.620 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
what happens, you know, this is
a tale of two different police

29:14.653 --> 29:18.890 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
departments. But the police
department in Washington got

29:18.924 --> 29:21.593 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
