they figured this out?

29:21.627 --> 29:23.595 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ARMSTRONG: It did. They were
confronted with the fact that

29:23.629 --> 29:26.798 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
they had made a mistake of
dramatic proportions. Not only

29:26.832 --> 29:29.568 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
had they not believed a woman
who had, indeed been raped. They

29:29.601 --> 29:31.570 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
had gone further and they had
punished her. They had filed a

29:31.603 --> 29:33.572 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
citation charging her with false
reporting. So, they had to find

29:33.605 --> 29:35.574 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
her and go and tell her that she
had been right all along. They

29:35.607 --> 29:37.909 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
now recognized that. And they
tried to find out ways that they

29:37.943 --> 29:40.012 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
could prevent this from
happening again. They ordered an

29:40.045 --> 29:46.318 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
independent review and external
review to reconstruct the ways

29:46.351 --> 29:51.356 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
in which they had gone off the
rails in this investigation.

30:02.834 --> 30:06.204 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SREENIVASAN: So, do police
departments around the country

30:06.238 --> 30:11.009 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
keep track of how many rapes are
reported, how many people recant

30:11.043 --> 30:14.646 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
this? Because it seems like in
the general arc of domestic

30:14.680 --> 30:17.783 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
violence, that this would be a
common occurrence, that people

30:17.816 --> 30:21.353 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
say, "yes, he hit me", something
happened and they were perhaps

30:21.386 --> 30:24.089 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
